column5: Hey guys, heading up to Dogtooth Lake with the wife June 3-10. Anyone else going to be fishing there that week? It will be my first trip there. Just wondering if any of you veterans of the lake will be around to give a guy some pointers on where to find some fish. I did get lake map from Rushing River that has the coordinates to a lot of the rocks on the lake. Has anyone else used this map and enter the coords into your Humminbird? Thanks for any info
